divs: Sighting DetailsMy mother and I were walkin up to our appartment on the side walk and i lookedup and saw a light in the sky. i stood for about 10 seconds, just looking atthis thing. It was going south west in a sort of snake like pattern. My mom askme what i was doing than she looked up as well. about 15 seconds after shelooked we both saw it stop, it was really up there and than it had stopped andwas stationary for another 20-25 seconds, than it shot off going the exactopposite direction wich would have been north east. and to this day we stilltalk about it. 1 more person saw it but he thinks im dumb writing it in to youfolks. I would be eager to hear from someone if there have been any othersightings of it that night in or around Winnipeg, Manitoba, Canada. Thank you
